import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import SendIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Send';

function ChatInput() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <InputContainer>
                <form>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Message here..." />
                    <SendButton>
                        <Send />
                    </SendButton>
                </form>
            </InputContainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default ChatInput
